{"tid":361712,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"c朗要求水,法庭給他可樂被拒,法官逐給自己的水給c朗","createTime":"2017-08-16T10:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T12:04:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b0fc7c15e2aa7a7521530d3de025dec3c803ca9","tid":361712,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"皇馬當家球星c朗出席了稅務案法庭陳述。西班牙媒體科貝電台透露了法庭上的一個小細節，在庭審時c朗拒絕碳酸飲料。<br />\n\t<br />\n\t科貝表示，西裝革履的c朗在在陳述時，由於屋內空氣悶熱，葡萄牙隊長出了不少汗，因此他脫下來自己的外套並且向法官請求喝水。<br />\n\t<br />\n\t當有人向c朗遞上一瓶可樂的時候遭到了他的拒絕，皇馬當家球星堅持要白水，最後法官將自己的礦泉水遞給了c朗。"},{"pid":"bda1ea129d2b58caa3c13f477810685f5211c0f3","tid":361712,"uid":4747,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"咁撚麻煩架"},{"pid":"1e572bf11574318e9754a567e9d5c8180b2143d6","tid":361712,"uid":27163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2475f51604d0f457d2cbcf41a940eb81effaa6b3","tid":361712,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇馬當家球星c朗出席了稅務案法庭陳述。西班牙媒體科貝電台透露了法庭上的一個小細節，在庭審時c朗拒絕碳酸飲料。<br />\n\t<br />\n\t科貝表示，西裝革履的c朗在在陳述時，由於屋內空氣悶熱，葡萄牙隊長出了不少汗，因此他脫下來自己的外套並且向法官請求喝水。<br />\n\t<br />\n\t當有人向c朗遞上一瓶可樂的時候遭到了他的拒絕，皇馬當家球星堅持要白水，最後法官將自己的礦泉水遞給了c朗。</blockquote><br />\n由於屋內空氣悶熱<br />\n家事法庭？"},{"pid":"aeb8dd622750ee37560b0ab28bd95e557491e9e3","tid":361712,"uid":2295,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚麻煩架</blockquote><br />\n飲可樂係運動員大忌黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbc4ba39a2290601fea7c338a9e70d32e383e64","tid":361712,"uid":1256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"又想show肌"},{"pid":"cb7d9507697212e06024d8753e48a4f5afffd69d","tid":361712,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又想show肌</blockquote><br />\n比啲壓力法官同陪審團"},{"pid":"6529c83fb2268a9273f749a2778091258a3279a1","tid":361712,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"山區兒童無可樂飲"},{"pid":"3a583e8ffc42e73daca36a1a851401afe5846016","tid":361712,"uid":11314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山區兒童無可樂飲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d922597265fc0f0dff1f67020a2882ffa4a39b","tid":361712,"uid":30699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"想飲啖水姐 咁都要寫鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd06f59ef5b27fa1965fe3ad3958c02fe38a39e8","tid":361712,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山區兒童無可樂飲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d921de29610f51cea1725f55be2947922cbaaab8","tid":361712,"uid":19714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山區兒童無可樂飲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為贊助問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ce43929138e62b46da2199ff602d4c8e08081","tid":361712,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:05:07.000Z","msg":"C朗咁職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eb8cf6c7b14f549b3982af8859d39d2fbe0a27","tid":361712,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"果然係好想keep住自己身體最佳狀態 連碳酸飲品都一滴不侵"},{"pid":"a56eaf1ed9afcda94c97317f4346e999310410